abstract: >
  OSIRIS / DNA::}{::lang SDK v6.0.0 is a quantum-native CLI and multi-language
  SDK with an integrated Non-Local Non-Causal Language Model (NCLM) cognitive shell.
  Gen 6 features 24 new NCLM modules including an autonomous research knowledge graph
  (35 nodes, 6 edge types), hypothesis engine, and paper writer. Key scientific result:
  θ_lock = 51.843° = arccos(1/φ_golden) confirmed to 0.016° angular precision,
  establishing θ_lock as the golden ratio partition angle in 11D CRSM geometry.
  UQCB negentropic operation confirmed at τ_Revival = φ^8 = 46.978μs by two
  independent simulations. Hardware validation: Bell F=0.9473, CHSH S=2.690 on
  127-qubit IBM Fez. CAGE Code: 9HUP5.
